{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01SmektBF985aso1EamnKZzK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_014vAcH28SUJsZvaxSH8c7QL","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Update ObjectMapper injections","prompt":"I need you to update all Java files in the project at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output that inject an unqualified ObjectMapper (without @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper) to use @Named(\"wrapRootValue\") qualifier instead.\n\nThe files that need to be changed are:\n1. ArticlesResource.java - has both `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\")) and `@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper ObjectMapper noWrapObjectMapper;` (keep as-is)\n2. UserResource.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n3. UsersResource.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n4. ProfilesResource.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n5. BusinessExceptionMapper.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n6. BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n7. InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n\nFor each file:\n1. Read the file\n2. Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;` if not already present\n3. Change the injection from:\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   OR\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   private ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   to:\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   @Named(\"wrapRootValue\")\n   ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   or\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   @Named(\"wrapRootValue\")\n   private ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   \nNote: Do NOT change injections that already have @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper qualifier.\nNote: In ArticlesResource.java, only the FIRST unqualified ObjectMapper needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"), the second one that has @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper should NOT be changed.\n\nMake ALL these changes now.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1096,"cache_read_input_tokens":120507,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1096,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":693},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2092f313-8131-46b3-b954-3b9c381a11ae","uuid":"b1f9a2b5-2d5e-4d04-bc7b-9cd47afb8afb"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need you to update all Java files in the project at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output that inject an unqualified ObjectMapper (without @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper) to use @Named(\"wrapRootValue\") qualifier instead.\n\nThe files that need to be changed are:\n1. ArticlesResource.java - has both `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\")) and `@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper ObjectMapper noWrapObjectMapper;` (keep as-is)\n2. UserResource.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n3. UsersResource.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n4. ProfilesResource.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n5. BusinessExceptionMapper.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n6. BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n7. InfrastructureExceptionMapper.java - has `ObjectMapper objectMapper;` (needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"))\n\nFor each file:\n1. Read the file\n2. Add `import jakarta.inject.Named;` if not already present\n3. Change the injection from:\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   OR\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   private ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   to:\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   @Named(\"wrapRootValue\")\n   ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   or\n   ```\n   @Inject\n   @Named(\"wrapRootValue\")\n   private ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n   ```\n   \nNote: Do NOT change injections that already have @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper qualifier.\nNote: In ArticlesResource.java, only the FIRST unqualified ObjectMapper needs @Named(\"wrapRootValue\"), the second one that has @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper should NOT be changed.\n\nMake ALL these changes now."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014vAcH28SUJsZvaxSH8c7QL","session_id":"2092f313-8131-46b3-b954-3b9c381a11ae","uuid":"23cae39a-3409-4576-bcf0-b284e43f9183"}
