{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01KYBGncZFsp4Gmwndxziaa7","type":"tool_result","content":"=== RealWorld API Smoke Tests ===\nTesting against: http://localhost:33791/api\n\n--- Test 1: GET /api/tags ---\n[PASS] GET /api/tags returns 200\n--- Test 2: GET /api/articles ---\n[PASS] GET /api/articles returns 200\n--- Test 3: POST /api/users (register) ---\n[PASS] POST /api/users returns 201\n--- Test 4: POST /api/users/login ---\n[PASS] POST /api/users/login returns 200\n--- Test 5: GET /api/user (authenticated) ---\n[PASS] GET /api/user returns 200 with auth\n--- Test 6: PUT /api/user (update bio) ---\n[PASS] PUT /api/user returns 200\n--- Test 7: POST /api/articles (create article) ---\n[PASS] POST /api/articles returns 201\n--- Test 8: GET /api/articles/{slug} ---\n[PASS] GET /api/articles/smoke-test-article-1773473836 returns 200\n--- Test 9: POST /api/articles/{slug}/comments ---\n[PASS] POST /api/articles/smoke-test-article-1773473836/comments returns 200\n--- Test 10: GET /api/articles/{slug}/comments ---\n[PASS] GET /api/articles/smoke-test-article-1773473836/comments returns 200\n--- Test 11: POST /api/articles/{slug}/favorite ---\n[PASS] POST /api/articles/smoke-test-article-1773473836/favorite returns 200\n--- Test 12: GET /api/profiles/{username} ---\n[PASS] GET /api/profiles returns 200\n--- Test 13: POST /api/users/login (invalid credentials) ---\n[PASS] POST /api/users/login with invalid creds returns error\n--- Test 14: GET /api/user (unauthenticated) ---\n[PASS] GET /api/user without auth returns 401\n\n=== Results ===\nTotal: 14 | Passed: 14 | Failed: 0\nSMOKE TESTS: ALL PASSED","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2092f313-8131-46b3-b954-3b9c381a11ae","uuid":"f558dfe0-fbf7-4f6b-8792-dccd062f1e43"}
